SATURDAY 5 SEPTEMBER 2020 (DAY 29)
CHRIS MCGAHAN, USA 🇺🇸
(McGahan Peluso Ministries)

Chris illustrates how God works His plan of redemption in people’s lives through putting pieces of broken glass together, creating a valuable piece of art! Chris’ Redento Raffinato signature vases have been commissioned for such dignitaries as former Vice-President Dick Cheney and for the Donald J. Trump Christian Inaugural Gala in Washington D.C.

SUNDAY 6 SEPTEMBER 2020 (DAY 30)
MARY ANN PELUSO-MCGAHAN, USA 🇺🇸
(McGahan Peluso Ministries)

Mary Ann has worked closely with David Wilkerson, serving as his soloist. Mary Ann was a soloist at the Jimmy Swaggart Ministries singing in televised crusades both stateside and internationally.

MONDAY 7 SEPTEMBER 2020 (DAY 31)
KLEMEN VIDIC, SLOVENIA 🇸🇮
(Krščanski Center)

Klemen was raised in an atheist home and as a teenager struggled to find the meaning of life. But in a supernatural encounter with Jesus in July 1992, the course of his life was forever transformed. Jesus spoke to Klemen in an audible voice saying “I am alive!” He realized he had just discovered the meaning of life he was searching for - Jesus! Klemen knows God is all we need and continues to share this truth with the Slavic nations and throughout world.

